Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Summary", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"82b1ca7a-ff99-4136-b633-88e0b6fe3c2d"],

Cell["\<\
This notebook has verified:
  1. Each P, SV, SH eigenvector satisfies A.v = \[Lambda]v (Section 6)
  2. The symplectic inverse Dz^(-1) = -i J6.Dz^T(-kx,-ky).J6 (Sections 8, 12)
  3. The spectral decomposition A = Dz.\[CapitalLambda].Dz^(-1) [EQUATION \
(3.12)] (Section 9)
  4. Numerical spot check confirms machine-precision agreement (Section 10)
  5. Quasi-Hamiltonian symmetry of A (Section 11)

All identities are verified SYMBOLICALLY \[Dash] they hold for arbitrary (\
\[Rho], \[Alpha], \[Beta], \[Omega], kx, ky).\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"bae23b64-7e61-43c7-8261-259e29b1224c"]
}, Open  ]]
